ABOUT_LOVERINO_COPY_1: Loverino is a different type of dating service. Despite from other similar services, it is not possibile to match with more than one person.
ABOUT_LOVERINO_COPY_2: Loverino is targeting those people that are serious about their dating activity. As it does not allow to have more that a match at the time, it will probably mostly used by people with more serious dating intentions.
ABOUT_LOVERINO_COPY_3: Are you looking for getting lucky for a day, you will probably not find loverino as the right choice for you. This opens up to those user that are searching for deeper relationships.
COOKIE_POLICY_1: We want you to feel safe about the way loverino treats your data. Loverino cares about your intergrity and will therefore give you more details about how data is used.
COOKIE_POLICY_2: Loverino stores your user data in a cookie. This is done in order to make it easier to give you a great user experience. Data is not shared with other providers. Moreover, no sensitive data is stored in the cookie.
CURRENTLY_IN_A_MATCH_CONSEQUENCES: Please note that you can not have more than a match. For this reason you won't see new suggestion as long as you have a match.
WARNING_PICTURE_REQUIRED: Please note that a profile picture is mandatory
